4,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T14:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澤村開外掛係好睇 <br />\n但係愈黎愈覺得作者乾塘<br />\n可能因為投手一場一個 冇得好SD 咁同場發威<br />\n而家只係 澤村威+降谷沈默 之後又互換表情不停loop</blockquote><br />\n呢D都唔緊要，神作都會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 位，<br />\n但係佢欠缺大部份神作有既激發人心既金句。 我就咁up SLam dunk都有一堆神到癲既金句。好喇，遠既唔講，<br />\n就連「王牌投手」呢D都會up兩句：「衹要真心想贏既人，先可以真正享受棒球既樂趣， 我都想你地贏，但係乜都未做之前就講冇可能冇可能降低士氣，我係冇可能講投手1號俾呢一種人。」<br />\n鑽A播左成百幾集都未有激發人心既金句。<br />\n金句對一套神劇係既咁重要。<br />\n<br />\n加上降谷同澤村爭ace都一樣爭左百集。。。宜家第二季漫畫仲玩呢味，我真係暈左係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b075192fc051ce0ba054d90bcc5f7abed82240c0","tid":151744,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"第71話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/5025132089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5025132089&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bd456f95\" target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/5025132089</a><br />\n😑"},{"pid":"2de4751dbd1097307c079974619ae1add87facc1","tid":151744,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第71話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/5025132089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5025132089&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8p7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=bd456f95\" target=\"_blank\">http://tieba.baidu.com/p/5025132089</a><br />\n😑</blockquote><br />\n降谷都算第一次比片岡咁話法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27f5f2f3235b7a7b4a2c8a6c9ae7baa81b59368","tid":151744,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T15:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第71話<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/p/5025132089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Fp%2F5025132089&d=Fe1Xron1K